OL,3,CGovernment 'failing to keep promise to
OL,4,Cchildren on mental health and housing'
OL,6,FThe Children's Rights Alliance says
OL,7,Fthe Irish government has failed to
OL,8,Fkeep its promise to children in
OL,9,Frelation to mental health, and is
OL,10,F"struggling to deliver effectively" on
OL,11,Fhousing.
OL,13,FThe organisation launched its Report
OL,14,FCard 2024 on Tuesday, which grades the
OL,15,Fcoalition government on the progress
OL,16,Fmade in commitments to children
OL,17,Fcontained in the Programme for
OL,18,FGovernment.
