OL,6,FThis is the fourth analysis of Fianna
OL,7,FFail, Fine Gael and the Green Party's
OL,8,Fpromises in 'Our Shared Future' ` and
OL,9,Fhow it performed for children in 2023
OL,10,Fby analysing 1,615 promises made to
OL,11,Fchildren and young people and rating
OL,12,Fthe Government's efforts.
