OL,3,CGovernment 'failing to keep promise to
OL,4,Cchildren on mental health and housing'
OL,6,FIt gave progress on child mental
OL,7,Fhealth services an E grade, the third
OL,8,Fconsecutive E grade in this area; a D
OL,9,Fgrade on ending Direct Provision; and
OL,10,Fa D minus grade on family homelessness
OL,11,Fdue to the record number of homeless
OL,12,Fchildnre, though it said "green
OL,13,Fshoots" are beginning to emerge on the
OL,14,Fissue.
OL,16,F"In 2023 we also saw the number of
OL,17,Fpeople leaving homeless accommodation
OL,18,Fand entering the private market fell
OL,19,Fto 58%, meaning that 42% exited to
OL,20,Fmore sustainable tenancies such as
OL,21,Fsocial housing," the Alliance said.
