OL,3,CGovernment 'failing to keep promise to
OL,4,Cchildren on mental health and housing'
OL,6,FChief executive of the Children's
OL,7,FRights Alliance Tanya Ward said it was
OL,8,F"an important year" for investing in
OL,9,Fpublic services for children, naming
OL,10,Fthe 4.7 million euro investment into
OL,11,Faffordable early years education, the
OL,12,Fexpansion of both the free school
OL,13,Fbooks scheme and the school meals
OL,14,Fprogramme.
OL,16,F"At the same time, the Government is
OL,17,Fstruggling to get ahead of demand on
OL,18,Fhousing, including for people seeking
OL,19,Fprotection," she said.
