OL,3,CGovernment 'failing to keep promise to
OL,4,Cchildren on mental health and housing'
OL,6,FOn housing and Direct Provision, Ms
OL,7,FWard said that almost 4,000 children
OL,8,Fin emergency accommodation, according
OL,9,Fto the latest figures, means that
OL,10,FIreland is "miles behind where we need
OL,11,Fto be" to house young people "whose
OL,12,Fworld is being reduced to one small
OL,13,Froom".
OL,15,FShe added: "We acknowledge that the
OL,16,FGovernment is working in difficult
OL,17,Fcircumstances particularly because of
OL,18,Fthe Russian invasion of Ukraine.
