OL,6,FOn children's mental health services,
OL,7,Fit said it was "worrying" the
OL,8,FGovernment committed to ending the
OL,9,Fpractice of admitting children to
OL,10,Fadult units, and four years later they
OL,11,Fwere stating it may not be the case
OL,12,Fthat Ireland will ever be able to stop
OL,13,Fchildren being put in adult facilities.
