OL,3,CGovernment 'failing to keep promise to
OL,4,Cchildren on mental health and housing'
OL,6,FMs Ward said: "Admitting children in
OL,7,Fadult units when they are in distress
OL,8,Fis very frightening for them. The
OL,9,FReport Card reveals that 12 children
OL,10,Fwere admitted in the last year. This
OL,11,Fis down from 20 in 2022. However,
OL,12,Fserious questions need to be raised
OL,13,Fabout the lack of CAMHS beds, with 50
OL,14,Fper cent of the admissions in 2023
OL,15,Fcaused by the lack of CAMHS capacity."
