OL,6,FMs Ward added: "It is also important
OL,7,Fto note new initiatives announced by
OL,8,Fthe Government that demonstrate their
OL,9,Fdesire to develop innovative
OL,10,Fprogrammes and solutions that work to
OL,11,Faddress the acute inequality
OL,12,Fexperienced by Traveller families,
OL,13,Fchildren with disabilities and those
OL,14,Fof ethnic minorities with investment
OL,15,Fin the Equal Participation Model at
OL,16,Fearly years and new guidelines on the
OL,17,Fuse of reduced school days.
